msgid "The Site Key must be in UUID format (e.g. af232e06-59c2-4810-b09d-7a2b25632d1b)."
msgstr "Il Site Key deve essere in formato UUID (ad es. af232e06-59c2-4810-b09d-7a2b25632d1b)."

#: build/crumbler-cookie-consent/crumbler-cookie-consent.php:246
#: crumbler-cookie-consent.php:264
msgid "Connect your website to the Crumbler cookie consent service."
msgstr "Collega il tuo sito web al servizio di consenso ai cookie Crumbler."

#: build/crumbler-cookie-consent/crumbler-cookie-consent.php:253
#: crumbler-cookie-consent.php:271
msgid "Optional settings for special requirements."
msgstr "Impostazioni facoltative per esigenze particolari."

#: build/crumbler-cookie-consent/crumbler-cookie-consent.php:267
#: crumbler-cookie-consent.php:285
msgid "Show Cookie Consent Widget on the website"
msgstr "Mostra il widget di consenso ai cookie sul sito web"

#. translators: %s: link to Crumbler Dashboard
#: build/crumbler-cookie-consent/crumbler-cookie-consent.php:279
#: crumbler-cookie-consent.php:297
#, php-format
msgid "You can find the Site Key in the %s under the respective site."
msgstr "Puoi trovare il Site Key nel %s, sotto il sito corrispondente."

#: build/crumbler-cookie-consent/crumbler-cookie-consent.php:290
#: crumbler-cookie-consent.php:308
msgid "Automatic (browser language)"
msgstr "Automatico (lingua del browser)"

#: build/crumbler-cookie-consent/crumbler-cookie-consent.php:301
#: crumbler-cookie-consent.php:319
msgid "When set to \"Automatic\", the widget detects the visitor's browser language."
msgstr "Con « Automatico » il widget rileva la lingua del browser del visitatore."

#: build/crumbler-cookie-consent/crumbler-cookie-consent.php:310
#: crumbler-cookie-consent.php:328
msgid "Only change if you run your own widget instance. Leave empty for default."
msgstr "Modifica solo se utilizzi una tua istanza del widget. Lascia vuoto per il valore predefinito."

#: build/crumbler-cookie-consent/crumbler-cookie-consent.php:320
#: crumbler-cookie-consent.php:338
msgid "Hide widget for logged-in administrators"
msgstr "Nascondi il widget per gli amministratori che hanno effettuato l'accesso"

#: build/crumbler-cookie-consent/crumbler-cookie-consent.php:441
#: crumbler-cookie-consent.php:471
msgid "Cookie Consent"
msgstr ""

#: build/crumbler-cookie-consent/crumbler-cookie-consent.php:449
#: crumbler-cookie-consent.php:479
msgid "Warning:"
msgstr "Attenzione:"

#: build/crumbler-cookie-consent/crumbler-cookie-consent.php:449
#: crumbler-cookie-consent.php:479
msgid "The widget is enabled but no Site Key has been entered. The widget will not work without a Site Key."
msgstr "Il widget è attivato ma non è stato inserito alcun Site Key. Senza Site Key il widget non funziona."

#. translators: 1: site name, 2: domain
#: build/crumbler-cookie-consent/crumbler-cookie-consent.php:472
#: crumbler-cookie-consent.php:502
#, php-format
msgid "Connected to Crumbler: %1$s is set up and active for %2$s. The widget is being served."
msgstr "Connesso a Crumbler: %1$s è configurato e attivo per %2$s. Il widget viene distribuito."

#. translators: %s: domain
#: build/crumbler-cookie-consent/crumbler-cookie-consent.php:479
#: crumbler-cookie-consent.php:509
#, php-format
msgid "Connected to Crumbler: this domain (%s) is set up and active. The widget is being served."
msgstr "Connesso a Crumbler: questo dominio (%s) è configurato e attivo. Il widget viene distribuito."

#. translators: %s: domain
#: build/crumbler-cookie-consent/crumbler-cookie-consent.php:492
#: crumbler-cookie-consent.php:522
#, php-format
msgid "This domain (%s) is not authorised for the entered Site Key. Add it to the allowed domains of this site in your Crumbler dashboard. Until then the widget will not be displayed."
msgstr "Questo dominio (%s) non è autorizzato per il Site Key inserito. Aggiungilo ai domini consentiti di questo sito nella tua dashboard Crumbler. Fino ad allora il widget non verrà visualizzato."

#: build/crumbler-cookie-consent/crumbler-cookie-consent.php:496
#: build/crumbler-cookie-consent/crumbler-cookie-consent.php:501
#: build/crumbler-cookie-consent/crumbler-cookie-consent.php:506
#: crumbler-cookie-consent.php:526
#: crumbler-cookie-consent.php:531
#: crumbler-cookie-consent.php:536
msgid "Re-check now"
msgstr "Verifica di nuovo"

#: build/crumbler-cookie-consent/crumbler-cookie-consent.php:500
#: crumbler-cookie-consent.php:530
msgid "The Site Key is unknown to Crumbler, or this domain is not active yet (for example the subscription or trial is not set up). The widget will not be displayed until the domain is added and active in your Crumbler dashboard."
msgstr "Il Site Key è sconosciuto a Crumbler oppure questo dominio non è ancora attivo (ad esempio l'abbonamento o il periodo di prova non è configurato). Il widget verrà visualizzato solo quando il dominio sarà aggiunto e attivo nella tua dashboard Crumbler."

#: build/crumbler-cookie-consent/crumbler-cookie-consent.php:505
#: crumbler-cookie-consent.php:535
msgid "The Crumbler service status could not be verified right now (service unreachable). The widget script is still embedded on all pages."
msgstr "Non è stato possibile verificare lo stato del servizio Crumbler in questo momento (servizio non raggiungibile). Lo script del widget rimane comunque incorporato in tutte le pagine."

#: build/crumbler-cookie-consent/crumbler-cookie-consent.php:515
#: crumbler-cookie-consent.php:545
msgid "Save Settings"
msgstr "Salva le impostazioni"

