#: crumbler-cookie-consent.php:558
msgid "The cookie declaration displays all detected services and cookies, grouped by category. You can embed it in two ways:"
msgstr "La dichiarazione sui cookie mostra tutti i servizi e i cookie rilevati, raggruppati per categoria. Puoi integrarla in due modi:"

